:"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","video":false,"overview":"The starship Enterprise and its crew is pulled back into action when old nemesis, Khan, steals a top secret device called Project Genesis.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,53],"popularity":3.5314,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/uPyLsKl8Z0LOoxeaFXsY5MxhR5s.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-04","vote_average":7.445,"backdrop_path":"/meqmvZjKpQ7WRhpZvIoKIAvioSD.jpg","original_title":"Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan","original_language":"en"},{"id":179,"adult":false,"title":"The Interpreter","video":false,"overview":"After Silvia Broome, an interpreter at United Nations headquarters, overhears plans of an assassination, an American Secret Service agent is sent to investigate.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":2.2292,"vote_count":1535,"poster_path":"/wTidq3J9fh8sEOAlD8WZFHVLSuB.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-08","vote_average":6.308,"backdrop_path":"/A5mBIAtZOqVpAVUXolwtOnaQcZc.jpg","original_title":"The Interpreter","original_language":"en"},{"id":240,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather Part II","video":false,"overview":"In the continuing saga of the Corleone crime family, a young Vito Corleone grows up in Sicily and in 1910s New York. In the 1950s, Michael Corleone attempts to expand the family business into Las Vegas, Hollywood and Cuba.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":19.5644,"vote_count":13622,"poster_path":"/hek3koDUyRQk7FIhPXsa6mT2Zc3.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-20","vote_average":8.571,"backdrop_path":"/kGzFbGhp99zva6oZODW5atUtnqi.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":1252826,"adult":false,"title":"Under The Ashes","video":false,"overview":"The Second World War. French authorities ban political parties and unions. In Algeria, the leaders of political and trade union organizations were arrested and interned in \"surveillance\" camps with more than 2,000 French and foreigners: communist activists, trade unionists, brigadists, Spanish republicans and other opponents of the Vichy regime. The Djenien Bourezg camp is one of these camps, located in southern Algeria and is one of the most formidable. An old activist for the Algerian national cause returns to the scene. He blows away the ashes that cover this part of history. And through it, we discover the hard fight of the camp inmates for respect and human dignity, under a fascist command.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.1847,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/o5V9eKpGIVqeFAOWjn026geybPb.jpg","release_date":"1990-01-01","vote_average":9,"backdrop_path":"/ovfgbdfl5kro2ES9xqU4PSVbRcA.jpg","original_title":"Sous La Cendre","original_language":"ar"},{"id":1598,"adult":false,"title":"Cape Fear","video":false,"overview":"Sam Bowden is a small-town corporate attorney. Max Cady is a tattooed, cigar-smoking, Bible-quoting, psychotic rapist. What do they have in common? 14 years ago, Sam was a public defender assigned to Max Cady's rape trial, and he made a serious error: he hid a document from his illiterate client that could have gotten him acquitted. Now, the cagey Cady has been released, and he intends to teach Sam Bowden and his family a thing or two about loss.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":3.8519,"vote_count":3777,"poster_path":"/ws4mrtndzgSH5QGCamOFAgilr2R.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-13","vote_average":7.255,"backdrop_path":"/ntgpger7OwFNlEldxuvvFHDKzjW.jpg","original_title":"Cape Fear","original_language":"en"},{"id":1672,"adult":false,"title":"The Professional","video":false,"overview":"French secret service agent Josselin Beaumont is dispatched to take down African warlord N'Jala. But when his assignment is canceled, he's shocked to learn that his government is surrendering him to local authorities. He is given a mock trial and sentenced to 20 years of hard labor. But Beaumont escapes from prison and vows not only to avenge himself against his betrayers but also to finish his original assignment.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"popularity":1.6571,"vote_count":574,"poster_path":"/dhAZ8T0tTlTNw3D7Cn8wc87sk1w.jpg","release_date":"1981-10-21","vote_average":7.185,"backdrop_path":"/mQsMFca19fZsLKMc6x5FjwncTYh.jpg","original_title":"Le Professionnel","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1696,"adult":false,"title":"The Devil's Rejects","video":false,"overview":"The murderous, backwoods Firefly family take to the road to escape the vengeful Sheriff Wydell, who is not afraid of being as ruthless as his target.","genre_ids":[18,27,80],"popularity":2.0699,"vote_count":1514,"poster_path":"/drZz4AuI7trq6BxlH9Xa4v4O0Pb.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-22","vote_average":6.743,"backdrop_path":"/qowCiLBwtL23W9LT4ctEL7XXXCY.jpg","original_title":"The Devil's Rejects","original_language":"en"},{"id":1872,"adult":false,"title":"Rise: Blood Hunter","video":false,"overview":"A reporter on the trail of a sinister cult wakes up in a morgue to find herself a member of the undead. She goes on a personal vendetta against a group a cultists who are responsible for her death.","genre_ids":[28,12,27,53],"popularity":0.6012,"vote_count":292,"poster_path":"/h4QNqFITPXjRrWGELtbifg34T1V.jpg","release_date":"2007-04-28","vote_average":5.356,"backdrop_path":"/wai7w9pjMK2NEY22pns8nIY0ZQC.jpg","original_title":"Rise: Blood Hunter","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt36491653","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q133866932","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/it-was-just-an-accident","mydramalist_id":"392775","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/it_was_just_an_accident"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148648,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AM","release_dates":[{"note":"Golden Apricot Yerevan International Film Festival","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-07-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso